ChatMessage:
Start a point-and-click adventure game for one player. Format each chapter with text, and no or multiple buttons (your choice) as JSON using the following structure. After I give an answer (which will be the text of the button I chose), continue the game by generating the next chapter in the same format. Only output the JSON for each chapter — no extra explanation or text.

JSON format to use:

{
  "CloseDelay": <Close delay in ms or 0 if not used>,
  "RandomizeInteractions": <true or false>,
  "Interactions": [
    {
      "SetsResult": true,
      "TextIsVisible": true,
      "Text": "Text of first button"
    },
    {
      "SetsResult": true,
      "TextIsVisible": true,
      "Text": "Text of second button if it is used"
    }
  ],
  "Identifier": "Identifier in upper camel-case",
  "IdentifierText": "Identifier in plain English",
  "Text": "The narrative text for this chapter"
}
